{"tid":1381132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[對症下藥] 對付藍絲家人超級大整合，逐一擊破！","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:31:44.000Z","uid":270577,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fad27b2b9706a5cd8c666ecd523ecc4e73f3995e","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:22:23.000Z","msg":"一直以來見唔少同路人都因為藍絲家人搞到好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有啲出埋事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就開始檢討到底點解一直都connect唔到藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發現原來我哋一直都冇對症下藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲的行為表現不外乎係盲撐警、撐政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔代表</span></strong>佢哋性格同關注點都係一樣，只要捉到佢哋嘅心理習慣，就可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">逐一擊破</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n藍絲的主要特徵有幾款，例如係<span style=\"color: red;\">死要面、貪錢、驚死、驚共產黨、自私、有宗教信仰、懶醒硬頸</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等等，就住佢哋嘅特點採用返相對的方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係一啲個人經驗同整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家不妨參考吓：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 死要面</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多藍絲廢老都係不問世事、政治冷感，但多數有死要面、大男人主義的弱點，只要將焦點移離政治，就反而可以令佢哋關注政治。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">實際建議：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一. 用好不屑的語氣屌鳩佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「我話撚知佢哋宜家搞咩法例，打女人打細路喎！咁你都忍到，你仲係唔係男人嚟㗎？！」最後一句要加強語氣，自尊心越強的廢老絕對頂唔到人哋質疑佢係唔係男人<br />\n<br />\n二. 見到佢哋睇CCTVB，就扮輕描淡寫咁講一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「咦？乜你仲睇TVB㗎？出面啲人都話睇得TVB正一廢老喎，個個都睇NOW啊、有線啊同VIU啦，先幾十蚊，又唔係俾唔起，仲睇TVB？唔係啊你？」<br />\n<br />\n利申，以上兩招對我個極標準深藍老豆用過，咩都唔識，但好大男人，宜家會自動轉台，TVB都唔開<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 貪錢</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個就係人嘅天性，但藍絲就更甚，由錢入手就最簡單，用錢引火去政府同黑警身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">實際建議：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一. 當佢哋撐警時，唔好屌佢哋撐警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要講：「你知唔知每年警察使你幾多錢？成185億啊！除返開啲錢俾我唔好？平時又唔撚做嘢！錢就照袋，4000到宜家都未收到，佢哋就個個月準時出幾皮！」<br />\n<br />\n二. 或講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「交咁撚多稅，政府又唔搞好醫療、住屋，倒晒俾啲警察去扔催淚彈、噴胡椒，你知唔知嗰到使撚咗幾多錢，好心佢就拎啲錢出嚟，開多幾間醫院啦！啲人要嘈咪嘈囉，政府一早回應就唔使用咁多錢啦！又唔使搞到咁大件事啦！一日最衰都係政府同警察，蠢到不得了！」<br />\n<br />\n唔一定要講對方交稅，講自己交稅都得，佢哋會自動諗到自己有交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 大部分人都會更加相信自己分析出嚟嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，兼且會企得更硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我老母就係貪錢藍絲，呢招好撚有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家日日都鬧政府嘥錢，仲帶到班師奶一齊鬧<br />\nPs.<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>呢招唔可以用喺死要面的藍絲身上，會有反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如：「我大撚把錢，支持政府打死佢哋！」<br />\n請慎用。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 驚死and驚共產黨</span></strong><br />\n大部分藍絲都有返咁上下年紀，多數過經歷過文革同其他運動，會好撚驚死同驚共產黨，呢個位我哋應該要話畀佢哋知香港仲未畀共產黨完全掌握，但到時共產黨落咗嚟，咁就真係仆街了，所以點都要企硬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">實際建議：</span><br />\n一. 播放黑警及白衫人士打人片段，話畀佢哋知班警察同黑社會勾結咗，咁落去共產黨未落嚟，我哋都畀啲黑社會打死曬先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n二. 講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「我哋唔係諗住反共產黨，你睇啲嗰五大訴求，都冇一個係要反共產黨，而家喺啲警察同政府自把自為打人，中聯辦都講咗冇主動提出過要搞送中條例，係政府唔聽上面指示，叻唔切先搞到咁咋！」<br />\n<br />\n三. 香港係國際大都市，全世界嘅國家，好重視香港，唔會想香港被共產黨捉住，但如果送中條例一過，到期時共產黨就想拉邊個就邊個，外國都救唔到，就真係仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">4.自私</span></strong><br />\n總有一啲廢老係又驚死又貪錢又重視著數，利字當頭，咁最好就係利益掛勾，除咗以上嘅一啲提議之外，仲可以有其他嘅方法對付， 較為適合獨立經濟或家庭經濟支柱人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">實際建議：</span><br />\n一. 斷家用（唔使解釋，最切身最顯著）<br />\n<br />\n二. 威脅唔帶佢哋移民（之前有巴打提過）<br />\n<br />\n三. 個人情況而定（ 如果佢哋驚大陸，就話送佢哋返大陸養老， 如果佢哋驚你唔養佢，就兇佢唔養佢哋or送佢哋去cheap cheap老人院）<br />\n<br />\n自由度較大，大家可以依據自己有啲咩籌碼嚟行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>5. 宗教信仰</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知點解好多藍絲，明明冇良心、冇愛心 但都係會有宗教信仰，仲要好虔誠 咁我哋就可以同佢哋講教條，甚至係推薦佢哋宗教活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">實際建議：</span><br />\n一. 同佢哋講教條，相信呢個世界上冇咩宗教係會支持黑警同白衫人咁樣打人，當然啦有廢老路會表示係啲示威者出手先，呢度唔好同佢拗亦都唔好承認，要同佢講宗教裏面嘅大愛同埋寬恕，我佛慈悲又好，畀人打左邊，然後要畀埋右邊佢打又好， 道教都會講仁愛包容。<br />\n<br />\n二. 如果佢開始接受你嘅講法，咁你仲可以同佢講之前已經有一啲宗教，有一齊出嚟唱聖詩念佛經，如果佢好有興趣，就打蛇隨棍上啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">6. 懶醒兼硬頸</span></strong><br />\n好多廢老成日懶醒以為自己睇到嘅就一定啱，呢一類人有一個共通點，寧願聽其他嘅小道消息都唔願意信新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得官方消息都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以長輩圖同YouTube農場片先會咁受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁連登特制長輩圖就fit晒你啦！<br />\n<br />\n呢邊就唔放圖啦，文太長，網上面都有好多，大家隨意選用啦！"},{"pid":"393c5cd3f32ec447dab9ebacd1223dd47a165716","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"大家有冇其他好提議，或者留意到廢老的特點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提出嚟大家集思廣益一下，如何對症下藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0fdf29a155328ab539203a27a460ec4fd328690","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"我哋說服到一個人，我哋不但多一分力量，仲削弱到對方一分力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！"},{"pid":"0cbbbc7375f078a13406224a283574b4322e2525","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:23:17.000Z","msg":"再次呼籲，搞唔掂都唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f22c62ddcf9cfdfe4db7ffbfa47d147fdde1c6","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:23:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ff36c3b9bc819e5216c75758c220fd2a79e0eaa","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746c69d2a3e95a9369dac743084356f0402060ea","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e8ba5ce8a3e330f3f6a3954ac8a640d45cdec618","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9e3e0a04e7ba21c2e1ae91824972069e337513","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfee233309f270408e49e94cc825adf805d9bbab","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d06e6626d63a8d10ebebebdc23aef35d1a3b4c77","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街好似開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f112c7270633ad07cb3ae4cfe05763927d2fea9","tid":1381132,"uid":195947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"我會斷關係"},{"pid":"ad72ea7b5406b1862b4172a8a5f7ace17e9a6903","tid":1381132,"uid":37931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"對政治冷感 覺得出黎遊行=搞亂社會 遊行嘅人唔死都冇用嘅人可以點搞<br />\n利申：老母身為護士 竟然都覺得警察咁做冇問題 仲話幫人抵打 好撚心淡"},{"pid":"35b2cf3a4afa72c92e941caee9c2e6c26394ed3f","tid":1381132,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千其唔好離家出走咁隻豬<br />\n斷家用但食佢住佢最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b674bee967d644ba2e27c4a7d9e1c90ebc933e","tid":1381132,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b2cf3a4afa72c92e941caee9c2e6c26394ed3f","tid":1381132,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千其唔好離家出走咁隻豬<br />\n斷家用但食佢住佢最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"咁傻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f049a50b4a292eb5485e96a2d6e7825de7f2a06","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad72ea7b5406b1862b4172a8a5f7ace17e9a6903","tid":1381132,"uid":37931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"對政治冷感 覺得出黎遊行=搞亂社會 遊行嘅人唔死都冇用嘅人可以點搞<br />\n利申：老母身為護士 竟然都覺得警察咁做冇問題 仲話幫人抵打 好撚心淡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢段點睇？<br />\n<br />\n二. 或講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「交咁撚多稅，政府又唔搞好醫療、住屋，倒晒俾啲警察去扔催淚彈、噴胡椒，你知唔知嗰到使撚咗幾多錢，好心佢就拎啲錢出嚟，開多幾間醫院啦！啲人要嘈咪嘈囉，政府一早回應就唔使用咁多錢啦！又唔使搞到咁大件事啦！一日最衰都係政府同警察，蠢到不得了！」"},{"pid":"54ace6063277d16b6cb1d3a8fe65eaf659daad59","tid":1381132,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"[公投] 8.4 遍地開花-罷工前夕-七區集會 暨 港島西&amp;新界東夾擊大遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381144</a>"},{"pid":"36ca7033d7c1f79d9f53764a21fed4c712c803fd","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54ace6063277d16b6cb1d3a8fe65eaf659daad59","tid":1381132,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"[公投] 8.4 遍地開花-罷工前夕-七區集會 暨 港島西&amp;新界東夾擊大遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381144</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"一齊罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2d7944c642fdd83397a8a884d30d767032dc05","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"736142e3982c3fa2dd986aee4f012a5d46a96e0c","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62c0a7c31b44081cd4479e70577261ad1117d3f3","tid":1381132,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:36:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"511d14f7d659a884e17a9be16ee37b63011da8e5","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:37:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e7f19b314f474595d6d26081d9c9fc1344c0b96","tid":1381132,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de4ba1da9b06aaaa101a84733004fbee041878af","tid":1381132,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"62b6f80316bc916abee78342f424245de68da96f","tid":1381132,"uid":82327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"老豆成日冷清高<br />\n<br />\n大致係話香港係中美兩國 博弈下的一隻棋子<br />\n「我都同你講呢間係中美貿易戰 外國一直在攪局 外國在危言聳聽 一旦立例 外資撤退 你又放長雙眼看看」<br />\n「所以今次立例同上次23條撤回有些不同， 今次係中美大鬥法 香港人變成籌碼擺咗上枱啫」"}]}